-- =============================================================================
-- Authors:        Thomas B. Preusser
--
-- Entity:				 Universal Asynchronous Receiver Transmitter (UART) - Receiver
--
-- Description:
-- -------------------------------------
-- :abbr:`UART (Universal Asynchronous Receiver Transmitter)` Receiver:
-- 1 Start + 8 Data + 1 Stop
--
-- License:
